rows.label: tlk43310141_05_msg0001
rows.name:
These Divine Beasts are packing
some awesome power.
But it has its limits.

rows.label: tlk43310141_05_msg0002
rows.name:
If there are many more clashes like that
between Invidia and Superbia...well...

rows.label: tlk43310141_05_msg0003
rows.name:
...all their power will be spent. And
that'll be it for this country.

rows.label: tlk43310141_05_msg0004
rows.name:
We think of Superbia as the enemy.
But if the Divine Beast goes down, then a
whole lot of people are going to die.

rows.label: tlk43310141_05_msg0005
rows.name:
That's not something I
really like to think about.

rows.label: tlk43310141_05_msg0006
rows.name:
We should've tried to sort this out
when we still had time to do it.
